{
  "texts": [
    "As shown in Figure 4, GPT-4 is particularly accurate in predicting scores similar to those of human respondents in the ISCO-08 major groups 3 Technicians and Associate Professionals (0.93), 9 Elementary Occupations (0.93), 5 Services and Sales Workers (0.92) and 2 Professionals (0.90).",
    "Only two major groups have a correlation below 0.80: 4 Clerical Support Workers (0.72) and 8 Plant and Machine Operators and Assemblers (0.75).",
    "X Figure 4: Correlations between GPT-4 generated and survey OSV scores across ISCO-08 major groups",
    "These initial observations indicate that GPT-4 has a strong grasp not only of the OP hierarchy, which might be somewhat expected given that OP is an established sociological concept, but also of the OSV hierarchy, where research is only emerging (Graeber 2018; Soffia et al. 2022; Walo 2023).",
    "The justifications GPT-4 provides in the first round of predictions allow some insight into its reasoning."
  ]
}